Print Toning in CMY Color Head Exposure adjustment in Source EXIF info on the Original thumbnail Film Profile name on the Last Edits thumbnail Significantly improved stability and performance Print Toning is widely used in photography to give a special character or atmosphere. As a natural evolution of the CMY Color Head it s based on split printing through color filters where you can control the color temperature separately in shadows midtones and highlights.
